tmpl_hh_wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"tmpl_hh_header\">\n        <div class=\"tmpl_hh_header__die\">\n            <img class=\"tmpl_hh_header__logo\" src=\"https://hhcdn.ru/ichameleon/162029.svg\" alt=\"\">\n            <img class=\"tmpl_hh_header__slogan\" src=\"https://hhcdn.ru/ichameleon/162028.png\" alt=\"\">\n            <a class=\"tmpl_hh_header__button\" href=\"https://hh.ru/article/27846?from=button_read\" target=\"_blank\">More information</a>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tmpl_hh_content\">\n       <strong>Job Description</strong> <p>OneAPI Data Analytics Library (oneDAL) team is looking for a Machine Learning Engineer. oneDAL is a powerful library for data scientists that turns large data clusters into meaningful information with advanced analytics algorithms.</p> <p>You will have a unique opportunity to work in the most promising and rapidly developing area of artificial intelligence and big data analytics and be one of the first who can observe how new technologies change the world around us.</p> <p>In this role you will be responsible for development, validation and optimizations of Graph Analytics algorithms for modern Intel architectures, integration of them into the customer's applications.</p> <p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p> <ul> <li> <p>Experience in C and C++ languages</p> </li> <li> <p>Strong mathematical/stat background and knowledge in graph analytics area</p> </li> <li> <p>Basic knowledge in machine learning area</p> </li> </ul> <p><strong>The following qualifications would be an added advantage:</strong></p> <ul> <li> <p>Knowledge of Windows &amp; Linux development environment</p> </li> <li> <p>Knowledge of Intel development tools and libraries</p> </li> <li> <p>Understanding of floating point operations and IEEE754 standard</p> </li> <li> <p>Knowledge of OpenCL/SYCL languages</p> </li> <li> <p>Knowledge of parallelism in shared (Intel TBB, OpenMP) and distributed (Intel MPI, Apache Spark, Dask) memory</p> </li> </ul></div>\n    <div class=\"tmpl_hh_icons tmpl_hh_flex\">\n        <div class=\"tmpl_hh_icons__item tmpl_hh_icons__item1\">\n            <div class=\"tmpl_hh_icons__image\"><img src=\"https://hhcdn.ru/ichameleon/162032.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n            <p class=\"tmpl_hh_icons__text\">Работа в динамично развивающейся области</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"tmpl_hh_icons__item tmpl_hh_icons__item2\">\n            <div class=\"tmpl_hh_icons__image\"><img src=\"https://hhcdn.ru/ichameleon/162030.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n            <p class=\"tmpl_hh_icons__text\">Решение интересных прикладных задач, применяемых в реальных проектах (мирового уровня), возможность увидеть результат своей работы, как это работает и применяется на практике</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"tmpl_hh_icons__item tmpl_hh_icons__item3\">\n            <div class=\"tmpl_hh_icons__image\"><img src=\"https://hhcdn.ru/ichameleon/162031.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n            <p class=\"tmpl_hh_icons__text\">Высокий профессиональный уровень сотрудников, эксперты с мировым именем и многолетним опытом</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"tmpl_hh_icons__item tmpl_hh_icons__item4\">\n            <div class=\"tmpl_hh_icons__image\"><img src=\"https://hhcdn.ru/ichameleon/162033.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n            <p class=\"tmpl_hh_icons__text\">Возможность заниматься исследовательской деятельностью совместно с представителями команд из других стран, выступать на профессиональных конференциях</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"tmpl_hh_icons__item tmpl_hh_icons__item5\">\n            <div class=\"tmpl_hh_icons__image\"><img src=\"https://hhcdn.ru/ichameleon/162034.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n            <p class=\"tmpl_hh_icons__text\">Открытая и дружная атмосфера в коллективе, всесторонняя <br>поддержка</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div> \n\n","vacancy_constructor_template":null,"key_skills":[{"name":"C/C++"},{"name":"Mathematical Statistics"},{"name":"Mathematical Modeling"},{"name":"Ma